{"tid":865743,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"百厭女生用爺爺骨灰製曲奇　受害同學：餅乾中間有灰色薄片","createTime":"2018-10-17T10:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T04:00:07.000Z","uid":207957,"like":306,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"6352843621817a252ca9e35255a01a87f827201a","tid":865743,"uid":207957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"美國加州兩名高中學生在製作曲奇時，混入祖父的骨灰，然後請同學食用。事件中至少9名同學「中招」，有受害者表示，餅乾中有少許灰色的薄片。<br />\n<br />\n據《KCRA》報道，美國加州有兩名Da Vinci Charter Academy的高中學生，於10月4日帶了特製骨灰曲奇請同學食用。<br />\n<br />\n受害者Andy Knox接受訪問時表示，當時該名女同學主動問其想不想吃曲奇，坦言曲奇內有特別的餡料。他本以為這些餡料是毒品，於是便問這些曲奇是不是含有大麻之類的東西，但得到的答案卻令他十分驚訝：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">她說這不是大麻，而是她爺爺的骨灰，然後笑了起來。</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，但Knox照樣食用。他表示味道與普通餅乾差不多，但口感就像吃進沙子一樣，有些碎碎的東西在齒間。而且骨灰的份量不多，他只見到餅乾中間有少許灰色薄片。<br />\n<br />\nKnox又指，其實該名同學並非第一次提到爺爺的骨灰。該女同學曾表示，如果Knox願意與其他同學調位，就會送他骨灰。本來Knox認為女同學只是開玩笑，誰知女同學真的拿出了骨灰龕。<br />\n<br />\n現時美國警方正調查中，暫時未有人因而生理及心理上感到不適。而警方亦未檢驗餅乾是否真的含有骨灰成份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WG9VQZA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWG9VQZA.png&h=e70db577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2185116/%E7%99%BE%E5%8E%AD%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A8%E7%88%BA%E7%88%BA%E9%AA%A8%E7%81%B0%E8%A3%BD%E6%9B%B2%E5%A5%87%E3%80%80%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%A4%85%E4%B9%BE%E4%B8%AD%E9%96%93%E6%9C%89%E7%81%B0%E8%89%B2%E8%96%84%E7%89%87?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2185116%2F%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%258E%25AD%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%2588%25BA%25E7%2588%25BA%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%2581%25B0%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E6%259B%25B2%25E5%25A5%2587%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A4%2585%25E4%25B9%25BE%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2581%25B0%25E8%2589%25B2%25E8%2596%2584%25E7%2589%2587%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=Y3ZsFMX1E4J%2BgR5VcGcqDZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f441120c\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2185116/%E7%99%BE%E5%8E%AD%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A8%E7%88%BA%E7%88%BA%E9%AA%A8%E7%81%B0%E8%A3%BD%E6%9B%B2%E5%A5%87%E3%80%80%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%A4%85%E4%B9%BE%E4%B8%AD%E9%96%93%E6%9C%89%E7%81%B0%E8%89%B2%E8%96%84%E7%89%87?r=mcsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fox40.com/2018/10/15/outraged-parents-say-davis-student-shared-cookies-made-with-her-grandmothers-ashes/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffox40.com%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2Foutraged-parents-say-davis-student-shared-cookies-made-with-her-grandmothers-ashes%2F&d=Y3ZsFMX1E4J%2BgR5VcGcqDZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=d4220868\" target=\"_blank\">https://fox40.com/2018/10/15/outraged-parents-say-davis-student-shared-cookies-made-with-her-grandmothers-ashes/</a>"},{"pid":"0e8caf33e7e14b6d569febdcdeecc75f28797157","tid":865743,"uid":9708,"like":181,"dislike":1,"score":180,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:14:34.000Z","msg":"骨灰味既杏仁片"},{"pid":"ae2e1d44d3f2ca9ef6f9dcf2bfc323e2c4ae5459","tid":865743,"uid":205530,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:15:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff48ebbca28f5df2f65e9305dd6f4449981811f9","tid":865743,"uid":208364,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:15:07.000Z","msg":"整舊嘆下"},{"pid":"e7ee5937546b3dc797803b78ff2126aab2c70368","tid":865743,"uid":22692,"like":379,"dislike":2,"score":377,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:15:10.000Z","msg":"佢個同學好玩得"},{"pid":"4e1e9ff910d7d4112854fcb49347ae0794c0f401","tid":865743,"uid":61692,"like":448,"dislike":4,"score":444,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:16:44.000Z","msg":"懷念爺爺<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">的味道</span>"},{"pid":"dd72fb3f8961cbece1c69218ff6e2e1a7c66660c","tid":865743,"uid":19979,"like":295,"dislike":3,"score":292,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:17:32.000Z","msg":"永遠和爺爺在一起了呢"},{"pid":"388eebd